title: Ravens rally late, top Steelers 23-20 in overtime
text:
> Pennsylvania Ravens rally late, top Steelers 23-20 in overtime Baltimore Ravens wide receiver Michael Campanaro (15) scores a touchdown over Pittsburgh Steelers cornerback Antwon Blake (41) in the first quarter of an NFL football game, Thursday, Oct. 1, 2015 in Pittsburgh.
